{"tid":1173591,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"梅斯達菲：防守屬爭「霸」關鍵","createTime":"2019-05-27T08:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T12:10:37.000Z","uid":199590,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f73ca80cf28a8befbee1a2b4f4e070cd21215bba","tid":1173591,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:24:12.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】阿仙奴周三於歐霸盃決賽大戰車路士，兩軍陣中有不少進攻好手，但中堅梅斯達菲認為防守才是爭勝關鍵。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴今季防守表現差強人意，於英超失球比車路士多12球；當中梅斯達菲（Shkodran Mustafi）身為德國國家隊世界盃功臣，應是防線大佬，但曾多次犯錯導致失守。<br />\n<br />\n雖然如此，但梅斯達菲仍然認為防守是爭取歐霸盃冠軍的最重要一環：「勝負在於開局，看看哪支球隊的組織性更強。」他指，兩軍太熟悉對方，所以要避免犯錯，「肯定是一場非常緊要的比賽。」<br />\n<br />\n「作為後衛的工作是保持不失球，但當你做足了90%本份，另外10%讓對手入球，大家就會忘記那90%。」梅斯達菲指，他們在英超未能殺入前4，但有機會於歐霸盃把晉身歐聯這目標達成。"},{"pid":"0a6310a3b69ebfb002998dedd8f71e67915e5d81","tid":1173591,"uid":22488,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:27:37.000Z","msg":"由佢講出黎真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d68481fdfb8c4ee6569c973de2a61ebfb8307d1","tid":1173591,"uid":131369,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:28:44.000Z","msg":"當中梅斯達菲（Shkodran Mustafi）身為德國國家隊世界盃功臣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/083456_5008241d15cc131843edd3ecaa1fc7a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F083456_5008241d15cc131843edd3ecaa1fc7a4.jpg&h=95748211&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fff36e3f74986701840f16c34cff0660dbbf101f","tid":1173591,"uid":55531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:07:20.000Z","msg":"睇黎決賽佢會自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03f5249c9a8dc918b848d857598186a0dde30bc","tid":1173591,"uid":26862,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UsErbbC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUsErbb